nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 187 is the 165th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the ninety-fifth issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on February 6, 2019.

The latest news, in-depth features, and exclusive interviews for Star Wars fans! Continue the year-long countdown to Skywalker Saga's finale, as we tackle the tumultuous events of Star Wars: Attack of the Clones. With the return of Star Wars: The Clone Wars on the horizon, we profile famous clone troopers, and ask what went wrong for the Jedi Knights as the Republic came crashing down.
